name: Erika Escariz
text: Love coming to this place. Staff is always courteous and awesome. Amazing pizza and pastas. Amazing deals too.

name: Kassandra Merino
text: We waited quite a while for our seat but it was worth it. The pizza was good and the server was friendly. We enjoyed our experience and would go back again.

name: Brian Harner ULTIMATE 2
text: Service was good, presentation was good, workers should have used hair nets, no hair in my food thankfully. A smile would have been nice to see. Other than that, my experience was good.

name: Debolina Banerjee
text: Quick bite Italian joint where you will get standard pizzas and pastas in budget cost.

name: sam osta
text: Good food to enjoy quick bite

name: Kristina Phillips
text: I asked if the take Apple Pay - they said yes.  Ordered pizza. Was asked if I wanted anything else - no. After the pizza goes through the toaster a woman asked me which salad I wanted.  I asked, does it come with it?  Only if it comes with …More

name: Ed Kwok
text: Been getting our pizzas from here for years, but somehow a misunderstanding.   Prices have gone up and I do not appreciate being laughed at by a "dough slinger". Maybe it was he that didn't understand?  Tables were dirty and trash swept …More

name: mermaid17 best
text: Best macncheese I have had in my 22 years on this planet.

name: R Clarke
text: Pizza isn't always the best, but after a day of shopping, it's one of the quickest ways to get food in the mall.

name: Victor Dymond
text: What happened?!?! Their pizza used to be soooooo goooood! Now it's totally not worth the calories, go next door to Panda or across the way to McDonalds

name: don jae
text: Really do not enjoy the food here. Plenty of alternative italian eateries that offer a better experience.

name: Ayushi Gupta
text: Not someplace i would eat every day. Food is very greasy and does not taste all that good.
